Number 2391
Name Wondrous Grove
ASTRAL
FIXED_LIGHT
*DESCRIPTION_START
The cherry trees are like the bars of a cage- a prison or perhaps a
great ribcage instead, for their trunks, stripped of bark, are bone
white and marked by the touch of gray-green corruption. You think of
gangrenous wounds, the cough of a fever... the things in nature which
are a part of the world, but show no respect for the other parts...
which would grow and destroy unchecked until they even destroyed
themselves. You feel so dizzy, unable to see exactly what happened to
the water. You can see it, and yet, you cannot bring your logical mind
to understand where it is...
*DESCRIPTION_END
IFVAR MONINROOM < 5
        GENMON 193
ENDIF

IFPREVERB SCREAM -1
        IFVAR DANSC = 1
                CLEARVERB
                ECHO OTHERS %N screams!
                ECHO PLAYER Your scream carries you on wings of fear... across the stream...
                MOVE 2388
        ENDIF
ENDIF

CHANNEL 2152
REGION 183

IFVAR INTNUM3 ! 1
        RANDOM DUMMY1 1 100 0
        IFVAR DUMMY1 < 30
                ADD FLAG1 1
                IFVAR DISGUISED ! 1
                        IFVAR FLAG1 = 1
                                AFFECT 2388
                                ECHO ALL You see %n walk among the cherry trees, smelling the blossoms, apparently at total peace with %h environment.
                        ENDIF
                        IFVAR FLAG1 = 2
                                AFFECT 2388
                                ECHO ALL You see %n pluck a ripe cherry from a low branch and eat it, slowly, with obvious relish.
                        ENDIF
                        IFVAR FLAG1 = 3
                                AFFECT 2388
                                ECHO ALL %N beckons to you from across the stream, smiling happily.
                        ENDIF
                ENDIF
        ENDIF
ENDIF
